{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji30.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给戴毓本的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给戴毓本的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年10月10日）毓本同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月九日来信收到。大有进步，甚以为慰。我同意彭习梅兄入革大学习，但须他自己下决心。如他决来，可持此信和校方接洽入校事宜。此复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺问近好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十月十日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]戴毓本，杨开慧在湖南长沙福湘女校、岳云中学读书时的同学，五四运动后曾在毛泽东创办的自修大学学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]彭习梅，戴毓本的丈夫。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":10,"day":10}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":521,"page_end":521},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}